      <div class="article-top">
                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">Is achieving your goals as easy as crafting a collage of inspirational images? Find out WTF a vision board really is, and if you should make one yourself.</div>
                <header class="article-header">
          <div class="group-article-meta">
            <div
  class="field field-name-post-date"
  itemprop="datePublished"
  content="2013-06-12"
>
  June 12, 2013  <span class="separator">|</span> </div>
            <div class="field article-author-top" itemscope itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
  <span class="label">By </span>
    <a
    href="http://greatist.com/p/sarah-koppelkam"
    title="User profile of "
    class="username"
    about="http://greatist.com/p/sarah-koppelkam"
    typeof="sioc:UserAccount"
    itemprop="url"
  >
    <span itemprop="name">Sarah Koppelkam</span>
  </a>
   </div>
          </div>
          <h1 class="title" id="page-title" itemprop="name headline alternativeHeadline">#WTF Is a Vision Board?</h1>
        </header>
        <div class="top-share">
          <div class="group_share" data-recirc-section>
  <div class="share-buttons icons" data-origin="top">
    <div ng-controller="socialCtrl"
